headline: Cintas Corporation to Participate in Upcoming Investor Conference
summary: CINCINNATI, October 22, 2025--Cintas Corporation (Nasdaq: CTAS) announced that its Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, Scott Garula, Vice President and Treasurer - Investor Relations, Jared Mattingley and Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer, Jim Rozakis, will participate in the upcoming J.P. Morgan Ultimate Services Investor Conference in New York City, NY on Tuesday, November 18, 2025. Cintas management will participate in a fireside chat and will be available
